ef subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00955">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 31. 7. [1899]</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
